WEBVTT

00:02.176 --> 00:04.613
-PREVIOUSLY ON "OUTSIDERS"...

00:04.743 --> 00:06.658
-AAH!
DAMN IT, HAYLIE!

00:06.789 --> 00:08.312
MY FAMILY AND MY PRIVACY
HAVE BEEN INVADED.

00:08.443 --> 00:10.010
-THIS IS NOT A BUSINESS
FOR LITTLE GIRLS.

00:10.140 --> 00:11.359
[ GUNSHOTS ]
-AAH! DAMN!

00:11.489 --> 00:12.795
-IT'S A WAR.
[ EXPLOSION ]

00:12.925 --> 00:14.623
-WHOA!
-BUT AS WITH ANY WAR,

00:14.753 --> 00:16.842
THE EVENTUAL VICTOR'S GONNA
TAKE SOME DAMAGE ALONG THE WAY.

00:18.844 --> 00:20.411
-[ LAUGHS ]

00:20.542 --> 00:22.631
THEM COAL BOYS GONNA SHIT
WHEN THEY SEE WHAT WE'VE DONE.

00:22.761 --> 00:24.328
-SHOULD I CALL THE POLICE?

00:24.459 --> 00:26.200
-NO, THEY'RE USELESS.
THE NEW SHERIFF'S AN OXY FREAK.

00:28.158 --> 00:30.595
-CALEB! CALEB!

00:30.726 --> 00:31.901
WAKE UP.
-WHERE ARE WE?

00:32.032 --> 00:33.642
-IT'S ALL RIGHT.
EVERYTHING'S FINE.

00:33.772 --> 00:35.470
-IT'S NOT GONNA WORK, HASIL.
WE'RE TOO DIFFERENT.

00:35.600 --> 00:37.428
-I MEAN, SURE,
YOU'RE A WOMAN, I'M A MAN,

00:37.559 --> 00:39.604
BUT THAT SORT OF HELPS
THE SITUATION, DON'T IT?

00:39.735 --> 00:42.303
-WHERE YOU BEEN, BABY GIRL?
-I WENT TO NAOMI'S AFTER WORK.

00:42.433 --> 00:44.522
-WAS THE WHITE BOY THERE
WITH YOU?

00:44.653 --> 00:46.263
YOU LYIN' TO ME?
-NO, SIR.

00:46.394 --> 00:48.700
-SHE AIN'T GONNA BE MY WOMAN
THAT MUCH LONGER.

00:48.831 --> 00:50.137
SHE GONNA BE MY WIFE.

00:50.267 --> 00:53.053
-SHE'S A FINE, FINE WOMAN.

00:53.183 --> 00:57.361
I DON'T WANNA SEE YOU LOSING HER
TO SOME OTHER MAN.

00:57.492 --> 01:01.713
-I WANT HIM, BUT HE'LL HURT ME.

01:01.844 --> 01:03.889
HE'LL LEAVE AGAIN, I KNOW IT.

01:04.020 --> 01:05.369
I STILL LOVE HIM.

01:05.500 --> 01:08.372
-YOU KILLED MY BABY BROTHER.
-[ GRUNTS ]

01:08.503 --> 01:10.679
[ GUNSHOT ]

01:10.809 --> 01:13.725
-[ GROANING ]

01:13.856 --> 01:15.771
[ GUN CLICKS ]
-WE NEED REPEATERS, AUTOMATICS.

01:15.901 --> 01:17.207
-YOU THINK YOU KNOW
WHAT'S UP ON THAT MOUNTAIN,

01:17.338 --> 01:18.817
BUT YOU DON'T KNOW
A GODDAMN THING.

01:18.948 --> 01:21.690
'CAUSE IF YOU KNEW, YOU WOULDN'T
BE CHASING AFTER IT.

01:21.820 --> 01:24.606
YOU WOULD BE RUNNING.

01:26.782 --> 01:29.785
[ WIND WHISTLING ]

01:31.874 --> 01:35.704
-BOTH OF YA, LOOK ON ME.

01:35.834 --> 01:37.488
SEE WHAT YOU DONE?

01:37.619 --> 01:40.012
YOU GOT 'EM SHOOTIN' AT US
LIKE WE'RE CHICKENS IN THE PEN.

01:40.143 --> 01:41.536
THIS CHILD BE CRIPPLED.

01:41.666 --> 01:43.015
-THAT AIN'T NOTHING
BUT A FLESH WOUND, MOTHER.

01:43.146 --> 01:44.452
WON'T LIKELY LEAVE A MARK.

01:44.582 --> 01:46.541
-I'M GONNA BE LEAVIN' A MARK
ON YOUR SKULL

01:46.671 --> 01:48.325
YOU DON'T STOP
YOUR GUM FLAPPING.

01:48.456 --> 01:50.022
I'M ASHAMED OF BOTH OF YOU,

01:50.153 --> 01:52.634
GOING OFF LIKE A COUPLE OF
DRUNKEN STRAYS.

01:52.764 --> 01:54.331
-WE DID WRONG, MA'AM,

01:54.462 --> 01:56.377
AND WE BEG YOUR FORGIVENESS.

01:56.507 --> 01:58.901
-AND YOU?
-I AGREE. HE DONE WRONG.

01:59.031 --> 02:02.165
-IF I HAD MY STRENGTH,
I'D CUFF YOUR HEAD CLEAN OFF.

02:02.296 --> 02:04.472
-THERE'S TWO MACHINES
DOWN THERE.

02:04.602 --> 02:07.214
TWO MONSTERS THE SIZE OF
SUNRISE ROCK.

02:07.344 --> 02:09.172
I TURNED THEM TO JUNK.

02:09.303 --> 02:11.957
I STOPPED THEM COAL JACKANAPES
DEAD SOLID.

02:12.088 --> 02:14.917
AND WHAT DO I GET FOR MY REWARD?
A TONGUE LASHING.

02:15.047 --> 02:19.530
-THESE YOUNG'UNS, FOSTER,
FOR REASONS I CAN'T FIGURE

02:19.661 --> 02:23.099
GIVEN THE END OF ALL DAYS,
THEY LOOK UP TO YOU.

02:23.230 --> 02:26.407
LORD SPARE US,
THEY WANNA BE LIKE YA.

02:26.537 --> 02:31.673
YOU WANNA LEAD SOMEDAY?
START LEADING BY EXAMPLE.

02:31.803 --> 02:37.069
COAL FOLKS WON'T ALLOW THIS SIT.
WHAT WE GONNA DO?

02:37.200 --> 02:41.726
-FA WAS RIGHT. WE NEED FIRE.
WE NEED TO ARM OURSELVES SERIOUS

02:41.857 --> 02:45.469
OR WE WILL BE CHICKENS IN A PEN,
JUST LIKE YOU SAID.

02:45.600 --> 02:47.254
-WHAT'S YOUR CALL BACK TO THAT?

02:47.384 --> 02:49.778
-MY CALL IS THAT
WE SHOULD PREPARE, MA'AM.

02:49.908 --> 02:52.868
WE SHOULD BE READY TO FIGHT,
BUT THE TIME IS NOT NOW.

02:52.998 --> 02:58.439
-LONGER I LIVE,
LESS I UNDERSTAND.

02:58.569 --> 03:02.530
BUT THIS I DO KNOW --

03:02.660 --> 03:04.096
YOU'RE BOTH WRONG.

03:07.622 --> 03:09.624
AND STAY OFF THE WINE.

03:11.669 --> 03:13.584
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

03:13.715 --> 03:15.325
-ALL'S I'M DOING IS
ASKING YOU A QUESTION.

03:15.456 --> 03:16.848
-WELL, IT'S ALL A PART OF
THE SAME THING, WADE, ISN'T IT?

03:16.979 --> 03:18.415
-WHAT IS?
WHAT'S A PART OF THE SAME THING?

03:18.546 --> 03:20.112
-CALEB WALKING IN HIS SLEEP.

03:20.243 --> 03:22.419
-YEAH, IT'S A MEDICAL CONDITION
AND IT RUNS IN FAMILIES.

03:22.550 --> 03:23.725
-WHO TOLD YOU THAT?

03:23.855 --> 03:25.117
-I LOOKED IT UP.
I LOOKED IT UP, LEDDA!

03:25.248 --> 03:27.207
-WADE, YOU FOUND HIM
MILES FROM HOME

03:27.337 --> 03:30.079
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT,
TALKIN' TO ANDI-RAE.

03:30.210 --> 03:31.863
-I-I KNOW, LEDDA.

03:31.994 --> 03:33.474
I MEAN, MAYBE THIS IS A PHASE
THAT HE'S GOING THROUGH.

03:33.604 --> 03:35.127
-OH, A PHASE?
-YEAH, MAYBE IT'S A PHASE.

03:35.258 --> 03:37.695
-WADE, LOOK, I LOVE YOU.

03:37.826 --> 03:39.436
I LOVE YOU
AND YOU'RE MY BROTHER,

03:39.567 --> 03:42.352
BUT YOU GOTTA GET SOME HELP.

03:42.483 --> 03:44.485
YOU NEED TO GET RIGHT
WITH THE DRINKIN'

03:44.615 --> 03:46.400
AND WITH THE PILLS.

03:46.530 --> 03:47.705
-THANK YOU VERY MUCH
FOR THE CAKE.

03:47.836 --> 03:49.316
-WADE, LISTEN.
WADE! LISTEN TO ME!

03:49.446 --> 03:50.926
-GET YOUR HAND OFF ME, LEDDA.

03:51.056 --> 03:53.320
-NO, YOU'RE GONNA LISTEN
TO WHAT I HAVE TO SAY, WADE!

03:53.450 --> 03:55.974
-GET OFF ME.
-YOU ARE! COME ON. JUST...

03:56.105 --> 03:59.064
[ CRYING ]

04:02.329 --> 04:04.026
[ SNIFFLES ]

04:04.156 --> 04:06.246
I CAN'T DO THIS ANYMORE.

04:06.376 --> 04:08.204
AND YOU GET SOME HELP,

04:08.335 --> 04:12.382
OR I'M TAKING THAT BOY
AWAY FROM YOU.

04:12.513 --> 04:15.559
♪♪

04:18.562 --> 04:20.521
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

04:33.490 --> 04:37.233
♪♪

04:37.364 --> 04:41.368
-♪ THE DAWN IS UP, THERE'S
FIRE ON THE MOUNTAIN ♪

04:41.498 --> 04:45.415
♪ THEY'LL HAVE TO ANSWER
FOR THEIR CROOKED PLAN ♪

04:45.546 --> 04:48.505
♪ THE HOLLOWS
WILL SURROUND THEM ♪

04:48.636 --> 04:50.855
♪ AND THEY'LL GO RUNNIN'

04:50.986 --> 04:54.294
♪ BACK TO THE WRETCHED REALM
THEY CAME ♪

04:56.470 --> 05:02.911
♪ NOR WILL THE DOGS OF HELL
REFRAIN ♪

05:03.041 --> 05:08.569
♪ AND THE LAND WILL SUFFER
THOSE WHO PAID ♪

05:13.965 --> 05:15.837
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

05:15.967 --> 05:18.187
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

05:19.406 --> 05:21.016
-GOOD MORNING, YOU.

05:21.146 --> 05:22.887
-MORNING.
-GUESS WHAT I JUST HEARD.

05:23.018 --> 05:24.541
OUR COUNTRY SHERIFF
IS YOUR BROTHER-IN-LAW.

05:24.672 --> 05:26.195
IS THAT TRUE?
-[ SCOFFS ] YES, MA'AM.

05:26.326 --> 05:28.893
-[ LAUGHS ] I HAD NO IDEA
HOW WELL-CONNECTED YOU WERE.

05:29.024 --> 05:30.547
-MY WIFE LEDDA IS HIS SISTER.

05:30.678 --> 05:32.854
-WELL, COME TAKE A LOAD OFF.

05:32.984 --> 05:34.769
WHY IS HE SO UNINTERESTED
IN GETTING THOSE PEOPLE

05:34.899 --> 05:36.248
OFF THAT MOUNTAIN?

05:36.379 --> 05:39.774
IT'S LIKE HE'S ON THEIR SIDE
OR SOMETHING.

05:39.904 --> 05:41.776
-DID YOU EVER HEAR
WHAT HAPPENED TO THEIR DADDY?

05:41.906 --> 05:43.386
-WELL, DO TELL.

05:43.517 --> 05:46.781
-WELL, BACK IN '89, ANOTHER
COMPANY -- BILOXI COAL --

05:46.911 --> 05:49.392
TRIED GETTING THE FARRELLS
OFF OF THAT LAND.

05:49.523 --> 05:53.048
WADE AND LEDDA'S DADDY WAS
A LINE BOSS FOR BILOXI.

05:53.178 --> 05:56.573
AND THEY SENT HIM UP THERE TO
TRY TO NEGOTIATE A SETTLEMENT.

05:56.704 --> 05:58.270
THINGS WENT WAY WRONG.

05:58.401 --> 06:01.361
SOME FARRELLS GOT SHOT.
TWO OF THEM DIED.

06:01.491 --> 06:03.101
AND A COUPLE DAYS AFTER THAT,

06:03.232 --> 06:04.712
WADE AND LEDDA'S DADDY
GOT KILLED

06:04.842 --> 06:06.191
ON HIS WAY HOME FROM WORK.

06:06.322 --> 06:08.803
-WHAT, THEY SHOT HIM?

06:08.933 --> 06:10.370
-HE GOT HIT BY LIGHTNING.

06:10.500 --> 06:11.719
-I'M NOT SURE I'M SEEING
THE CONNECTION.

06:11.849 --> 06:13.373
-WELL, NEITHER DO I.

06:13.503 --> 06:15.810
BUT SOME FOLKS IN THIS TOWN,
WADE BEING ONE OF THEM,

06:15.940 --> 06:19.204
THINK THAT THE FARRELLS...

06:19.335 --> 06:23.078
-WHAT? CONTROL THE ELEMENTS?
-IT WAS A SUMMER'S NIGHT.

06:23.208 --> 06:25.689
FOLKS SAY THERE WASN'T
A CLOUD IN THE SKY.

06:25.820 --> 06:30.564
-OH, LORDY, THIS IS
AN INTERESTING PLACE.

06:30.694 --> 06:32.348
-MS. GRIMES,

06:32.479 --> 06:34.176
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I'M DOING HERE.

06:34.306 --> 06:36.134
THIS FEELS REAL WEIRD,
SITTING IN THIS OFFICE,

06:36.265 --> 06:37.832
GETTING PAID FOR NOTHING.

06:37.962 --> 06:40.530
-WELL, YOU EARNED YOUR PAY
TODAY, BREECE.

06:44.882 --> 06:47.885
[ DRILL WHIRS ]

06:58.026 --> 06:59.636
[ DOORKNOB RATTLES ]

07:31.233 --> 07:33.409
-WHAT PART OF
"THEY TRIED TO POISON US"

07:33.540 --> 07:34.671
DO YOU NOT UNDERSTAND?

07:34.802 --> 07:37.369
-VANESSA, WE GOT LIGHTS,

07:37.500 --> 07:39.502
CAMERAS, MOTION DETECTORS.

07:39.633 --> 07:42.462
WE GOT A GUARD OUT THERE 24/7.

07:42.592 --> 07:45.073
WHAT WOULD YOU LIKE ME TO DO?
QUIT MY JOB?

07:45.203 --> 07:46.683
-YES!

07:46.814 --> 07:48.206
OR GET A TRANSFER OR SOMETHING.

07:48.337 --> 07:49.991
-IF I GO IN THERE
ASKING TO BE RELOCATED,

07:50.121 --> 07:51.775
I'LL LOOK LIKE
THE WORLD'S BIGGEST WUSS.

07:51.906 --> 07:54.648
-[ SCOFFS AND LAUGHS ]
-IT'LL BE THE END OF MY CAREER.

07:54.778 --> 07:58.347
-YOU EVER THINK
THAT MIGHT BE A GOOD THING?

07:58.478 --> 08:01.524
-MAN! THAT TAKES A LOAD OFF.

08:01.655 --> 08:04.309
I DON'T HAVE TO WORRY ABOUT
THE MORTGAGE OR, UH,

08:04.440 --> 08:07.312
CAR PAYMENTS,
HEALTH CARE, TUITION.

08:07.443 --> 08:09.532
THANKS!

08:09.663 --> 08:11.099
[ DISH CLATTERS ]

08:12.753 --> 08:16.278
-THEY'RE FREE.

08:16.408 --> 08:18.498
THE FARRELLS.

08:18.628 --> 08:21.239
-[ CHUCKLES ] WHAT?

08:21.370 --> 08:24.982
-FREER THAN WE'LL EVER BE.

08:25.113 --> 08:27.507
MAYBE I SHOULD JUST
MOVE UP THERE,

08:27.637 --> 08:30.118
IF I CAN GET PAST
OUR ARMED GUARD.

08:30.248 --> 08:32.860
[ RESUMES SCRUBBING DISHES ]

08:32.990 --> 08:34.688
-BUZZ AROUND.
-NO, IT'S NOT SO, OKAY?

08:34.818 --> 08:37.168
IT'S NOT HOW I LIKE TO DO IT.
-WHAT IF WE NEED TO SPLIT UP?

08:37.299 --> 08:38.735
-WE AIN'T.
THAT AIN'T HOW IT HAPPENS.

08:38.866 --> 08:40.737
-YEAH, BUT IF WE NEED TO
IS ALL I'M SAYING BECAUSE --

08:40.868 --> 08:43.523
-HEY, HEY, HEY, OOH, OOH.
[ CONVERSATION STOPS ]

08:43.653 --> 08:46.526
-OH, DON'T STOP TALKING
ON OUR ACCOUNT.

08:48.832 --> 08:52.183
YEAH, SEE, I KNOW Y'ALLS
ARE PLANNING A PARTY.

08:52.314 --> 08:54.490
AND SEEING AS I'M GONNA BE
THE ONE THAT HAS TO CLEAN UP

08:54.621 --> 08:56.753
THE BLOOD AFTERWARDS, I'D LIKE
TO KNOW WHAT THE PLAN IS.

08:56.884 --> 08:58.146
-AIN'T NO PLAN.

08:58.276 --> 09:01.715
-THAT'S WHAT WORRIES ME. SO?

09:06.807 --> 09:09.244
-IF THINGS GET OUT OF HAND,
I CAN TAKE CARE OF IT.

09:13.901 --> 09:15.293
-OKAY.

09:17.295 --> 09:20.124
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

09:20.255 --> 09:21.561
-YOU TELL HER ANYTHING?

09:21.691 --> 09:25.260
-NO. NOT A WORD.

09:25.390 --> 09:28.742
-ALL RIGHT.
HEY, CHECK THIS, BOYS.

09:30.744 --> 09:37.315
AH. THIS, YOU AIN'T SEEN SINCE
YOU WAS A LITTLE BITTY KID.

09:38.708 --> 09:40.318
OH. [ SIGHS ]

09:45.933 --> 09:47.674
MY FA'S.

09:47.804 --> 09:51.373
YEAH, LAST TIME A COAL COMPANY
COME AFTER US,

09:51.503 --> 09:53.462
THEY HAD RIFLES, CARBINES,

09:53.593 --> 09:56.857
THINGS SPITTING BULLETS
LIKE VENOM FROM A SNAKE.

09:56.987 --> 09:59.294
MY FA...

09:59.424 --> 10:00.774
THIS...

10:00.904 --> 10:03.385
THIS IS ALL HE HAD.

10:03.515 --> 10:07.128
THEY SHOT HIM IN THE THROAT.

10:07.258 --> 10:10.392
I RUN TO HIM,

10:10.522 --> 10:13.874
AND HE TRIED
TO TELL ME SOMETHING,

10:14.004 --> 10:17.660
AND THE ONLY THING TO COME OUT

10:17.791 --> 10:19.706
WAS BLOOD.

10:19.836 --> 10:21.751
[ EXHALES ]

10:26.364 --> 10:29.280
HE WASN'T JUST USING THIS

10:29.411 --> 10:31.892
TO SEND THEM
COAL FOLKS A MESSAGE.

10:32.022 --> 10:35.635
HE WAS SENDING
A MESSAGE TO US, TOO.

10:35.765 --> 10:37.637
'CAUSE THIS HERE?

10:37.767 --> 10:40.857
THIS IS THE PATH TO SALVATION.

10:40.988 --> 10:43.991
AND THE TIME IS NOW.

10:44.121 --> 10:46.646
NOW WE GOTTA LINE OUR PATH

10:46.776 --> 10:49.300
WITH THE MOST POWERFUL FIRE
WE CAN GET OUR HANDS ON,

10:49.431 --> 10:51.085
AND LOTS OF IT.

10:51.215 --> 10:53.130
-BIG OLD GUN SHOP OFF 22.

10:53.261 --> 10:54.784
I WAS SPYING ON IT
DAY 'FORE LAST.

10:54.915 --> 10:57.265
TRUCK PULL UP, A WHOLE LOT
OF BOXES COME OUT.

10:57.395 --> 11:01.399
TOOK THREE MEN A LONG SPELL
TO GET THEM ALL INSIDE.

11:01.530 --> 11:03.880
-WELL, GOOD. ALL RIGHT.

11:04.011 --> 11:06.317
THEN WE'RE GONNA GO DOWN
IN THE MORNIN'.

11:06.448 --> 11:09.669
TWO FULL DAYS FROM NOW.

11:09.799 --> 11:12.759
-W...WHY ARE WE WAITIN'?

11:12.889 --> 11:14.674
WHY NOT GET RIGHT DOWN THERE,
SNATCH UP THEM GUNS?

11:14.804 --> 11:17.111
-THIS IS HIS FIRST RUN.
HE'S ALL HARD FOR IT.

11:17.241 --> 11:20.941
-YEAH. WELL, LISTEN,
YOU GOTTA BE SMART, TICE.

11:21.071 --> 11:23.900
TWO DAYS AWAY,
THAT'S THEIR CHURCHIN' DAY.

11:24.031 --> 11:27.512
UH...EARLY IN THE MORNING,
WON'T BE NOBODY OUT AND ABOUT.

11:27.643 --> 11:31.778
YOU WANNA RIDE WITH US, SON?
YOU GOTTA BE THINKIN'.

11:31.908 --> 11:34.781
-YEAH, I'LL BE THINKIN'.
YOU'LL SEE. I'LL BE THE HERO.

11:34.911 --> 11:36.608
-[ SNORTS ]

11:36.739 --> 11:38.088
-I'LL BRING BACK SO MANY GUNS,
Y'ALL BE CALLING ME A MULE.

11:38.219 --> 11:39.481
-I'M THINKING THAT ALREADY.

11:39.611 --> 11:41.135
[ LAUGHTER ]

11:41.265 --> 11:43.615
HEY.

11:43.746 --> 11:46.836
TO THE MEMORY OF MY FA.

11:46.967 --> 11:48.664
-FOSTER FARRELL V.

11:48.795 --> 11:50.710
-UH-HUH.
[ LIQUID SPILLS ]

11:50.840 --> 11:54.061
-GED-GEDYAH.
-GED-GEDYAH.

11:54.191 --> 11:56.063
[ ALL SLURPING ]

11:56.193 --> 11:59.109
-[ TRILLS AND WHOOPS ]

11:59.240 --> 12:02.199
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

12:11.426 --> 12:14.168
[ SIREN WAILING ]

12:14.298 --> 12:16.910
[ TIRES SCREECH,
ENGINE TURNS OFF ]

12:17.040 --> 12:18.607
-WE TALK EVERY MORNING,
CLOCKWORK.

12:18.738 --> 12:20.914
TWO DAYS RUNNIN', I'M KNOCKIN'
AND KNOCKIN' AND NOTHING.

12:21.044 --> 12:22.393
LIGHTS ON ALL NIGHT.

12:22.524 --> 12:24.178
-MAYBE -- MAYBE HE'S DONE
GONE OUT OF TOWN, MA'AM.

12:24.308 --> 12:25.657
-HE DON'T GO OUT OF TOWN.
-THIS IS HIM? 102?

12:25.788 --> 12:27.398
-IF HE DID, I'D KNOWN
ABOUT IT, TRUST ME.

12:27.529 --> 12:29.879
NO, THEY CAME BACK FOR HIM.
-WHO'S THAT, MA'AM?

12:30.010 --> 12:31.663
-A WEEK AND A HALF AGO,
HE'S SHOOTING AT THEM FARRELLS.

12:31.794 --> 12:33.230
THEY WAS ROBBING
OUR NEIGHBOR HERE.

12:33.361 --> 12:34.623
-WELL, MA'AM, WE DIDN'T HEAR
ANYTHING ABOUT THAT.

12:34.754 --> 12:36.059
I GOT NO CALL ABOUT THAT AT ALL.

12:36.190 --> 12:37.582
-OH, WELL. YOU THINK
WE'RE CRAZY?

12:37.713 --> 12:39.149
YOU THINK WE WANT SOME
FARRELL-BRAND EVIL VOODOO

12:39.280 --> 12:40.760
RAINING DOWN ON US?

12:40.890 --> 12:43.110
NO. I HEARD A SHOT.
-OH, YEAH? YOU HEARD A SHOT?

12:43.240 --> 12:44.546
-I HEARD IT.
-MR. NICHOLS!

12:44.676 --> 12:45.939
-AND DON'T ASK ME
IF I DRINK 'CAUSE I DON'T.

12:46.069 --> 12:47.462
I HAVEN'T HAD A DROP
SINCE BICENTENNIAL.

12:47.592 --> 12:49.072
-ALL RIGHT, MA'AM, I'M
HEARING YOU. MR. NICHOLS,

12:49.203 --> 12:50.726
THIS IS COUNTY SHERIFF.
-NOW COME ON, GET IN --

12:50.857 --> 12:52.467
HE'S NOT GONNA ANSWER A KNOCK,
FOR CRYING OUT LOUD.

12:52.597 --> 12:54.295
-THIS IS COUNTY SHERIFF,
WADE HOUGHTON, MR. NICHOLAS.

12:54.425 --> 12:55.818
-JUST KICK IT IN,
FOR CRYING OUT LOUD.

12:55.949 --> 12:57.472
-ALL RIGHT, MA'AM,
CAN YOU STAND BACK, PLEASE?

12:57.602 --> 12:59.691
-WELL, HERE. NOW, GIVE IT A GOOD
KICK. WELL, NOW, COME ON.

12:59.822 --> 13:01.171
YOU CAN DO BETTER THAN THAT,
FOR GOD SAKES.

13:01.302 --> 13:02.825
I CAN DO BETTER THAN THAT.
-ALL RIGHT, MA'AM.

13:02.956 --> 13:04.261
-NOW, BUT -- GET THAT DOOR IN.

13:04.392 --> 13:05.915
-I'LL GO LOOK AROUND
THE BACK, ALL RIGHT?

13:06.046 --> 13:07.917
I'M GONNA ASK THAT YOU JUST
STAY HERE FOR A MOMENT.

13:08.048 --> 13:09.614
-NO, I'LL SHOW YOU
THE BACK DOOR 'CAUSE YOU --

13:09.745 --> 13:11.138
-OKAY, MA'AM, I DON'T NEED YOU
TO SHOW ME ANY BACK DOOR.

13:21.496 --> 13:23.367
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

13:25.456 --> 13:28.024
[ EXHALES ]

13:28.155 --> 13:32.072
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

13:42.256 --> 13:44.998
[ EXHALES ]

13:45.128 --> 13:49.132
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

14:19.162 --> 14:22.296
[ CONTINUES BREATHING HEAVILY ]

14:23.950 --> 14:26.169
-TRY TO BE, YOU KNOW,
HELP THINGS ALONG.

14:26.300 --> 14:27.518
MAKE IT MOVE FASTER.

14:27.649 --> 14:28.780
-WELL?

14:28.911 --> 14:31.174
-THAT'S A HEART ATTACK, MA'AM.

14:31.305 --> 14:34.699
-HEART ATTACK? NO. GOOD LORD,
IT'S NOT A HEART ATTACK.

14:46.015 --> 14:48.104
[ DOOR BELL JINGLES ]

14:52.108 --> 14:53.936
-[ Lowered voice ] HEY.

14:56.330 --> 14:58.810
WHAT'S THE MATTER?
I-I DO SOMETHING WRONG?

14:58.941 --> 15:00.290
-NO.

15:03.728 --> 15:06.253
-CAN I HELP YOU?
-NO! JUST...

15:07.602 --> 15:09.082
PLEASE LEAVE.

15:09.212 --> 15:10.692
-WHAT ARE YOU TALKIN' ABOUT?

15:10.822 --> 15:13.477
OKAY, I DON'T HAVE MUCH
EXPERIENCE WITH WOMEN...

15:13.608 --> 15:16.350
DOWN HERE. [ CHUCKLES ]

15:16.480 --> 15:20.615
SO EXCUSE ME IF I --
IF I SEEM A TOUCH CONFUSED,

15:20.745 --> 15:23.487
BUT...

15:23.618 --> 15:26.708
LAST TIME WE'S TOGETHER,
IT WAS BEAUTIFUL.

15:30.538 --> 15:34.150
-IT WASBEAUTIFUL.

15:34.281 --> 15:37.545
-THEN WHY YOU LOOK SO SAD?

15:37.675 --> 15:39.939
-HASIL...
-[ WOMAN SPEAKS INDISTINCTLY ]

15:40.069 --> 15:42.245
-[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

15:42.376 --> 15:44.421
I CAN'T SEE YOU ANYMORE.

15:47.685 --> 15:48.948
I'M SORRY.

15:49.078 --> 15:50.950
-YOU'RESORRY?

15:52.255 --> 15:55.345
YOU'RESORRY?

15:55.476 --> 15:57.782
-MY FAMILY'S NOT OKAY WITH IT.
-YOUR FOLKS?

15:57.913 --> 15:59.915
YOUR, UH, YOUR PARENTS?

16:00.046 --> 16:01.961
-MY BROTHER.

16:02.091 --> 16:05.007
-WHO CARES ABOUT YOUR BROTHER?
-MY MAMA RAN OFF YEARS AGO.

16:05.138 --> 16:06.966
I NEVER KNEW MY DADDY.

16:07.096 --> 16:11.144
MY BROTHER IS ALL I GOT,
AND HE IS NOT OKAY WITH THIS.

16:11.274 --> 16:13.755
-MAYBE I COULD GO
MAKE HIS ACQUAINTANCE.

16:13.885 --> 16:15.496
-HASIL, PLEASE.
-MAYBE I COULD TALK TO HIM.

16:15.626 --> 16:18.064
-THINGS WILL GET REAL BAD FOR ME

16:18.194 --> 16:20.457
IF WE ARE SEEN TOGETHER.

16:24.070 --> 16:26.115
-I AIN'T GONNA LET YOU GO.

16:26.246 --> 16:28.552
-LEAVE ME ALONE...

16:28.683 --> 16:31.991
[ Loudly ] YOU DIRTY, DISGUSTING
HILLBILLY.

16:32.121 --> 16:33.993
-[ PEOPLE MURMURING ]

16:34.123 --> 16:36.908
-YOU DON'T MEAN THAT.

16:37.039 --> 16:40.303
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

16:48.833 --> 16:52.141
-DID YOU SEE A GUNSHOT WOUND?
DID YOU SEE A STAB WOUND?

16:52.272 --> 16:54.796
DID YOU SEE ANYTHING THAT
COULD'VE CAUSED HIS DEATH?

16:57.146 --> 16:58.800
NO GUNSHOT WOUND?
NO STAB WOUND?

16:58.930 --> 17:00.367
THEN THEY SCARED HIM TO DEATH
IS WHAT.

17:00.497 --> 17:02.108
-YEAH, YOU WANT ME TO WRITE THAT
DOWN? "SCARED TO DEATH"?

17:02.238 --> 17:04.632
-DON'T MAKE FUN OF ME.
YOU GONNA BOOK HIM?

17:04.762 --> 17:06.025
HMM? CHECK FINGERPRINTS?

17:06.155 --> 17:07.461
-YES, I WILL CHECK
FOR FINGERPRINTS, MA'AM.

17:07.591 --> 17:08.940
I INTEND TO.
-WELL, NOW YOU'RE LYING TO ME,

17:09.071 --> 17:10.290
'CAUSE THEY AIN'T EVEN
IN THE SYSTEM.

17:10.420 --> 17:12.292
THEY DON'T GOT NO I.D.,
NO BARCODE.

17:12.422 --> 17:14.990
THEY RUN ROUGHSHOD OVER
THIS TOWN WITH TOTAL IMPUNITY.

17:15.121 --> 17:16.470
WHEN IS SOMEBODY GONNA DO
SOMETHING ABOUT IT?

17:16.600 --> 17:18.950
-MA'AM, MA'AM! [ CLEARS THROAT ]

17:19.081 --> 17:20.300
THERE'S NO EVIDENCE

17:20.430 --> 17:21.779
THAT ANYTHING HAPPENED
TO ANYBODY HERE

17:21.910 --> 17:23.477
EXCEPT AN OLD MAN
DONE FALL DOWN.

17:23.607 --> 17:25.827
-YEAH, EXCEPT FOR THAT GUNSHOT
I HEARD SO CLEAR.

17:25.957 --> 17:27.133
WELL, MAYBE I CALL
THE STATIES ON THIS.

17:27.263 --> 17:28.830
-YOU CALL THE STATIES, YEAH.

17:28.960 --> 17:30.136
YOU CALL THE STATIES,
THEY'RE GONNA REFER YOU TO ME.

17:30.266 --> 17:31.920
-WHAT A PIECE OF LUCK.

17:32.051 --> 17:33.791
OH, I'M GONNA REMEMBER THIS
COME ELECTION TIME, SHERIFF.

17:33.922 --> 17:36.185
-WHY DON'T YOU SHUT UP?!

17:36.316 --> 17:39.493
OLD BITCH!
YOU SHUT YOUR GODDAMN MOUTH.

17:39.623 --> 17:43.279
YOU STUPID OLD BITCH.
SHUT -- SHUT UP, YOU BITCH.

17:43.410 --> 17:46.587
[ WINDOW WHIRS ]

17:48.415 --> 17:51.244
♪♪

18:14.223 --> 18:17.096
[ GUN CLICKS ]

18:57.788 --> 19:00.835
-HELLO THERE.

19:00.965 --> 19:02.271
-WHAT YOU WANT, MAN?

19:02.402 --> 19:04.708
-MY NAME IS, UH,
IS HASIL FARRELL.

19:04.839 --> 19:08.756
-FARRELL?
-YEAH, THAT'S RIGHT. FARRELL.

19:08.886 --> 19:10.714
YOU MUST BE, UH, YOU MUST BE
SALLY-ANN'S BROTHER, RIGHT?

19:10.845 --> 19:14.979
YOU THE ONE
LOOKING OUT AFTER HER?

19:15.110 --> 19:18.809
THAT'S A RIGHT CARING THING
FOR YOU TO DO.

19:18.940 --> 19:20.333
-WHY DON'T YOU GET OUT OF HERE
BEFORE I KICK YOUR ASS?

19:20.463 --> 19:22.291
-NO NEED FOR THAT.
I JUST -- I CAME DOWN HERE.

19:22.422 --> 19:24.032
I JUST WANNA TALK TO YOU,
THAT'S ALL.

19:24.163 --> 19:25.425
I WANNA SHOW YOU
THAT I MEAN TO DO GOOD.

19:25.555 --> 19:28.906
I MEAN TO DO RIGHT. THAT'S IT.
LOOK, I...

19:29.037 --> 19:30.343
GOT YOU SOMETHIN'.

19:32.083 --> 19:33.520
[ OBJECT THUDS ]

19:33.650 --> 19:35.043
-YOU COME NEAR MY SISTER AGAIN,
I'LL KILL YOU.

19:35.174 --> 19:37.698
YOU HEAR ME?

19:37.828 --> 19:39.613
DAMN ANIMAL.

19:42.268 --> 19:44.661
[ Muffled voice ] WHAT'S
A FARRELL DOING AT THE DOOR?!

19:44.792 --> 19:46.185
WHY'S HE OUTSIDE?!
-WHY IS WHO OUTSIDE?

19:46.315 --> 19:47.838
-WHY YOU KNOW HIM?!
-I DON'T KNOW WHO --

19:47.969 --> 19:49.318
-SALLY-ANN!

19:49.449 --> 19:50.885
-WHY'S HE AT THE DOOR?!

19:51.015 --> 19:52.452
HEY! GET UP!
-NO!

19:52.582 --> 19:55.455
-HEY!
-WHAT?!

19:55.585 --> 19:58.284
-NO, STOP IT! NO, NO, NO!
NO, STOP!

19:58.414 --> 20:00.460
LEAVE HIM ALONE. JAMES!
JAMES, LEAVE HIM ALONE.

20:00.590 --> 20:02.679
-GET OFF ME! GET OFF ME!

20:02.810 --> 20:05.204
[ BOTTLE SHATTERS ]

20:05.334 --> 20:08.337
-[ GASPING
AND BREATHING HEAVILY ]

20:08.468 --> 20:11.558
-[ GRUNTS ]

20:11.688 --> 20:14.865
-YOU'RE HURTING HIM!
-[ GRUNTS ]

20:14.996 --> 20:17.999
-HASIL. HASIL, HASIL, STOP.
STOP. STOP, STOP!

20:18.129 --> 20:19.914
-[ GRUNTING ]

20:20.044 --> 20:21.394
[ WHACK ]

20:21.524 --> 20:22.786
-[ PANTING ]

20:22.917 --> 20:24.875
[ Whispering ]
YOU TOUCH HER AGAIN...

20:25.006 --> 20:26.486
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

20:26.616 --> 20:28.531
AND YOU'RE THE ONE
THAT'S GONNA BE DEAD.

20:28.662 --> 20:31.621
[ PANTING ]

20:33.232 --> 20:34.842
SALLY-ANN!

20:36.539 --> 20:38.193
SALLY-ANN!

20:43.590 --> 20:45.766
SALLY-ANN!

20:54.340 --> 20:56.255
[ SOFT KNOCK ON DOOR ]

21:02.870 --> 21:05.699
-I PUT A NEW LOCK ON YOUR DOOR.

21:05.829 --> 21:09.093
I CHANGED THE LOCKS ON --
ON ALL THEM DOORS.

21:13.663 --> 21:15.448
DO YOU KNOW -- YOU KNOW WHY?

21:19.582 --> 21:21.062
'CAUSE YOU'RE A...

21:21.192 --> 21:23.412
YOU'VE BEEN WALKING
IN YOUR SLEEP.

21:27.547 --> 21:29.288
YOU REMEMBER WHERE?

21:29.418 --> 21:32.160
-TO THE BUS STOP.

21:33.727 --> 21:35.076
-DOWN TO THE BUS STOP.

21:35.206 --> 21:38.340
YOU TOLD ME
YOU WERE TALKING TO MOM.

21:38.471 --> 21:40.386
REMEMBER THAT?

21:40.516 --> 21:43.606
I MISS HER, CALEB.

21:43.737 --> 21:45.913
YOU KNOW THAT?
I MISS HER VERY MUCH.

21:48.698 --> 21:52.223
HEY, LEAST WE KNOW
HOW YOU GOT THEM SCRATCHES.

21:52.354 --> 21:55.618
-I FELL IN A BUSH.

21:55.749 --> 21:58.055
MOM WAS THERE TO HELP ME UP.

21:59.970 --> 22:03.496
-YOUR MOM WAS THERE, TOO?
-IT MIGHT'VE BEEN A DREAM.

22:03.626 --> 22:04.975
I DON'T KNOW.

22:08.544 --> 22:12.156
-WELL, YOUR MOM LOVED YOU
VERY MUCH.

22:12.287 --> 22:15.682
-WHY DID SHE LEAVE?

22:15.812 --> 22:17.901
-UM... [ SIGHS ]

22:18.032 --> 22:20.861
SHE DIDN'T LEAVE.

22:20.991 --> 22:24.343
CALEB, SHE DIDN'T LEAVE.

22:24.473 --> 22:26.345
SHE WAS JUST SICK.

22:29.783 --> 22:32.220
SHE HAD A SICKNESS
IN HER HEAD.

22:40.359 --> 22:41.882
COME HERE.

22:44.450 --> 22:46.582
OKAY.

22:46.713 --> 22:48.323
SLEEP WELL.

22:50.151 --> 22:51.457
[ CLICKING ]

22:51.587 --> 22:54.808
-ARE YOU CLIPPING
YOUR TOENAILS IN THERE?

22:54.938 --> 22:56.244
-NO, DEAR.

22:56.375 --> 22:57.506
[ WATER RUNNING ]
-I FIND THE FRAGMENTS.

22:57.637 --> 22:59.203
IT'S HORRIFIC.

22:59.334 --> 23:01.728
[ WATER STOPS RUNNING ]

23:01.858 --> 23:03.033
NED?

23:03.164 --> 23:04.774
-I AM NOT CLIPPING MY TOENAILS.

23:04.905 --> 23:06.080
-THE WATER STOPPED.

23:06.210 --> 23:07.516
-JUST THE NEW HEATER ACTING UP.

23:07.647 --> 23:10.998
AIR IN THE LINER, SOMETHING.
GIVE IT A SECOND.

23:11.128 --> 23:14.393
-NO, IT'S STILL NOT WORKING.

23:14.523 --> 23:16.873
-I'LL CHECK IT.

23:37.764 --> 23:39.418
[ DOOR OPENS ]

23:40.680 --> 23:42.551
-[ Under breath ] WHAT THE...

23:42.682 --> 23:44.640
WHAT THE HELL?
[ SWITCH CLICKING ]

23:44.771 --> 23:46.642
DAMN IT.

23:46.773 --> 23:48.601
[ FLASHLIGHT CLICKS ]

23:55.085 --> 23:56.913
[ GUN COCKS ]
-OH.

23:57.044 --> 23:59.568
-SAY ONE WORD AND YOU'RE DEAD.

24:05.182 --> 24:06.706
-I SAID IT WAS YOU FARRELLS
BEHIND THIS.

24:06.836 --> 24:08.751
SHE DIDN'T BELIEVE ME.
-WHO IS THAT? HAYLIE GRIMES?

24:08.882 --> 24:10.361
OH, SHE'S A PRETTY LITTLE THING.

24:10.492 --> 24:13.756
HOPE SHE NEVER HAS KIDS, THOUGH.
SHE'LL PROBABLY EAT 'EM.

24:13.887 --> 24:17.368
NOW LET'S GET BACK
TO MY REQUEST.

24:17.499 --> 24:19.414
-I-I DON'T HAVE
THAT KIND OF POWER.

24:19.545 --> 24:20.894
-COME ON, NED. SURE YOU DO.

24:21.024 --> 24:23.462
YOUR ONE PLANET'S
GENERAL MANAGER OF OPERATIONS.

24:23.592 --> 24:26.639
YOU SIGNED THE CONTRACT.
IT'S ON THE WEB SITE, NED.

24:29.555 --> 24:31.731
ALL I NEED YOU TO DO
IS MAKE A PHONE CALL.

24:31.861 --> 24:34.473
TELL THEM WORK STOPS
ON THE ROAD, OKAY?

24:34.603 --> 24:36.866
I MEAN, I DON'T THINK ONE
PHONE CALL'S TOO MUCH TO ASK,

24:36.997 --> 24:38.520
IS IT, NED?

24:38.651 --> 24:40.304
ESPECIALLY WHEN YOU GOT A GUN
POINTED AT YOUR HEAD.

24:40.435 --> 24:41.958
-YOU BREAK INTO MY HOME. YOU TRY
TO POISON ME AND MY FAMILY.

24:42.089 --> 24:45.222
-OH, M.C.M.H. ISN'T FATAL, NED.
IT JUST STINGS A LITTLE.

24:45.353 --> 24:46.528
-I'VE NEVER HAD A PROBLEM
WITH YOU PEOPLE.

24:46.659 --> 24:48.617
LIVE AND LET LIVE.

24:48.748 --> 24:50.924
BUT YOU...

24:51.054 --> 24:52.491
SOMETHING ABOUT YOU AIN'T RIGHT.

24:52.621 --> 24:55.624
-OH, YOU'RE SMARTER
THAN YOU LOOK, MAN.

24:55.755 --> 24:59.410
-TELL YOU WHAT.
W-- YOU WANNA SHOOT ME?

24:59.541 --> 25:01.717
GO AHEAD. HUH? GO ON AND DO IT.

25:01.848 --> 25:03.850
-[ LAUGHS ] THAT --
THAT WAS VERY GOOD, NED,

25:03.980 --> 25:06.156
THAT A SMALL MOMENT
OF YOU HAVING SOME BALLS.

25:06.287 --> 25:07.941
BUT NOW THAT YOU'RE DONE,
YOU'RE GONNA GO UPSTAIRS,

25:08.071 --> 25:09.464
YOU'RE GONNA
CALL THE CONTRACTOR.

25:09.595 --> 25:11.205
YOU'RE GONNA TELL 'EM
WORK STOPS ON THE ROAD

25:11.335 --> 25:13.381
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY.

25:13.512 --> 25:14.817
-AND IF I DON'T?

25:16.602 --> 25:18.299
-[ SCOFFS ]

25:18.429 --> 25:21.302
NED, THERE WAS A TIME
WHEN I THOUGHT

25:21.432 --> 25:24.044
LIVING IN A SHACK WITH
NO RUNNING WATER OR ELECTRICITY

25:24.174 --> 25:26.960
WAS ABOUT THE LOWEST THING
A PERSON COULD BE SUBJECTED TO.

25:27.090 --> 25:28.831
I MEAN, THE SHAME I'D FEEL

25:28.962 --> 25:31.878
WHEN I WALKED PAST A HOUSE
LIKE THIS ONE,

25:32.008 --> 25:33.793
THE LOOKS I'D GET
FROM PEOPLE LIKE YOU.

25:35.446 --> 25:37.623
YOU EVER HAVE A MOMENT
WHERE YOU...

25:37.753 --> 25:40.451
WHEN YOU REALIZED
YOU'D SOONER DIE

25:40.582 --> 25:42.845
THAN TAKE ANOTHER
STINKING BREATH?

25:44.586 --> 25:47.110
MY GUESS IS NO, SO...

25:47.241 --> 25:49.243
I WIN.

25:49.373 --> 25:52.463
I MEAN, IF I SEE YOU
OR YOUR GUYS ON OUR MOUNTAIN,

25:52.594 --> 25:55.336
I'LL KILL YOUR SON
AND I'LL KILL VANESSA, TOO.

25:55.466 --> 25:57.947
AND THAT'D BE A SHAME
'CAUSE I LIKE THAT NAME.

26:00.471 --> 26:03.083
BALL'S IN YOUR COURT, NED.
OKAY?

26:09.785 --> 26:12.048
OH, AND JUST ONE MORE THING.

26:12.179 --> 26:13.833
-WHAT?

26:13.963 --> 26:16.879
-LOVE THE BOXERS.
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]

26:22.581 --> 26:24.234
-[ EXHALES ]

26:27.324 --> 26:28.543
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

26:28.674 --> 26:31.285
-YOU WERE DOWN THERE
A LONG TIME.

26:31.415 --> 26:33.940
I CHECKED A COUPLE SECONDS AGO.

26:34.070 --> 26:36.116
STILL NOT WORKING.

26:36.246 --> 26:38.553
-THAT'S -- THAT'S ALL RIGHT.

26:38.684 --> 26:40.729
COULDN'T -- COULDN'T FIX IT.

26:42.383 --> 26:43.732
-YOU OKAY?

26:43.863 --> 26:45.516
-YEAH.

26:45.647 --> 26:48.737
I'LL CALL A PLUM-- A PLUMBER
FIRST THING IN THE MORNING.

26:53.873 --> 26:55.570
[ WATER RUNNING ]
-BOOM. NED!

26:55.701 --> 26:57.224
[ TURNS OFF FAUCET ]

26:57.354 --> 27:00.749
IT'S WORKING!
HOW'D YOU DO THAT?

27:00.880 --> 27:02.446
[ BIRD CALLING ]

27:02.577 --> 27:07.408
[ DULCIMER PLAYING ]

27:07.538 --> 27:10.193
[ KNOCK ON DOOR, MUSIC STOPS ]

27:10.324 --> 27:11.542
-COME IN.

27:11.673 --> 27:14.850
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

27:14.981 --> 27:18.201
-I FOUND COUSIN JARED
SLEEPING OUTSIDE MY SHACK.

27:18.332 --> 27:22.292
SAID YOU NEEDED TO SEE ME,
SAID IT WAS URGENT.

27:22.423 --> 27:24.991
-WELL, I KNOW IT'S LATE.
WHERE YOU BEEN?

27:25.121 --> 27:27.863
-OH, YOU KNOW.
DOING MY USUAL GOOD WORKS.

27:27.994 --> 27:30.431
WHERE'S THE BELOVED
HUSBAND-TO-BE?

27:31.998 --> 27:34.087
-THERE'S SOMETHING GOING ON.
I NEED YOUR HELP STOPPING IT.

27:34.217 --> 27:37.699
-[ SCOFFS ] I CAN'T IMAGINE HOW
MUCH THAT PAINS YOU TO SAY THAT.

27:37.830 --> 27:39.396
-ASA.

27:39.527 --> 27:42.312
BIG FOSTER IS GOING AFTER GUNS.

27:42.443 --> 27:43.618
HE AND A COUPLE OTHERS,

27:43.749 --> 27:44.924
THEY'RE GOING DOWN
IN THE MORNING,

27:45.054 --> 27:47.274
THEY'RE GONNA ROB A GUN SHOP.

27:47.404 --> 27:48.928
-[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

27:49.058 --> 27:52.409
HOW MANY TIMES DID HIS MOTHER
DROP HIM ON HIS HEAD?

27:57.501 --> 28:00.722
WHAT -- WHAT DO YOU WANT ME
TO DO ABOUT IT?

28:00.853 --> 28:02.593
-WELL, IT'S HAPPENING
IN YOUR WORLD.

28:02.724 --> 28:04.944
DON'T YOU KNOW BETTER THAN
ANY OF US WHAT TO DO ABOUT IT?

28:05.074 --> 28:08.425
-OH, THIS IS GONNA BE
SOME KIND OF REWARD, HMM?

28:08.556 --> 28:11.341
-[ SIGHS ]
-IF I DO STOP 'EM?

28:11.472 --> 28:14.301
-ASA, YOU'RE NOT
DOING THIS FOR ME.

28:14.431 --> 28:16.912
YOU'RE DOING THIS
FOR ALL OF US.

28:17.043 --> 28:20.568
MAYBE YOU FORGOT THAT IT'S NOT
WEAPONS THAT KEEP US SAFE.

28:20.699 --> 28:22.265
IT'S NOT --

28:22.396 --> 28:25.225
IT'S NOT BULLETS THAT KEEP US
SURVIVIN' LONG WINTERS.

28:25.355 --> 28:26.661
THIS MOUNTAIN.

28:33.102 --> 28:35.975
-WHAT'S THE NAME OF
THE GUN SHOP?

28:36.105 --> 28:37.977
-UH, ALL'S -- ALL'S I KNOW

28:38.107 --> 28:41.241
IS IT'S A -- IT'S A-A BIG ONE
OFF 22.

28:41.371 --> 28:44.113
-H&S.

28:48.161 --> 28:50.816
ALL RIGHT, I'LL SEE
WHAT I CAN DO.

28:54.515 --> 28:56.604
[ DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES ]

29:07.006 --> 29:09.356
-LOOK AT YOU, ALL INDUSTRIOUS.

29:09.486 --> 29:11.575
I WENT BY YOUR HOUSE.

29:11.706 --> 29:13.360
YOUR LOVELY WIFE TOLD ME
YOU WERE HERE.

29:13.490 --> 29:15.362
-UM, SOMETIMES I COME IN
ON SUNDAY MORNINGS.

29:15.492 --> 29:16.755
IT'S, UH, IT'S QUIET.

29:16.885 --> 29:20.062
-WE HAVE A LOT MORE
TO DO NOW, DON'T WE?

29:20.193 --> 29:22.151
I GOT A CALL
FROM GUILLIAME BROTHERS,

29:22.282 --> 29:23.979
ASKING IF I KNEW ABOUT
LAYING OFF THE ROAD CREW

29:24.110 --> 29:25.285
STARTING MONDAY.
-MM-HMM.

29:25.415 --> 29:27.635
-I ASKED
WHEREVER THEY GOT THAT IDEA,

29:27.766 --> 29:29.245
AND THEY SAID THE ORDER
CAME FROM YOU.

29:29.376 --> 29:32.205
-IT'S TOTALLY TEMPORARY.
UH, WE JUST GOT SOME, UM...

29:32.335 --> 29:34.337
E.P.A. ISSUES TO SORT THROUGH.

29:34.468 --> 29:36.949
-YOU WANT ME TO CALL 'EM?

29:37.079 --> 29:38.733
-SURE. UM...

29:38.864 --> 29:41.127
LET ME GET THE --
OUR CONTACT OVER THERE.

29:41.257 --> 29:43.869
-IT'S WES HUTTON.
I'VE GOT IT RIGHT HERE.

29:43.999 --> 29:46.219
AND WHY DON'T YOUCALL
GUILLIAME BROTHERS,

29:46.349 --> 29:49.788
TELL THEM WE SPOKE,
AND GET 'EM STARTED UP AGAIN?

29:49.918 --> 29:52.442
-UM, NO.

29:52.573 --> 29:53.792
-EXCUSE ME?

29:55.663 --> 29:58.318
-I CAN'T.

29:58.448 --> 30:00.102
-AND WHY IS THAT?

30:00.233 --> 30:03.758
-IF I TELL YOU SOMETHING,
YOU HAVE TO PROMISE YOU WILL NOT

30:03.889 --> 30:06.369
GO TO CORPORATE SECURITY
OR THE POLICE.

30:06.500 --> 30:07.806
-WHY DON'T YOU TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON

30:07.936 --> 30:10.069
BEFORE I START MAKIN' PROMISES?

30:17.119 --> 30:21.384
-IT WAS A FARRELL,
BROKE INTO MY HOUSE --

30:21.515 --> 30:24.953
THE ONE THAT PUT THE METHYLCYCLO
INTO MY WATER TANK.

30:25.084 --> 30:26.607
-AND?
-HE PUT A GUN TO MY HEAD.

30:26.737 --> 30:30.393
HE SAID HE WOULD KILL
MY WIFE AND CHILD

30:30.524 --> 30:32.308
IF I DIDN'T STOP THAT ROAD.

30:32.439 --> 30:33.962
-THE FARRELLS SEEM TO HAVE
A PARTICULAR FASCINATION

30:34.093 --> 30:35.834
WITH YOU, NED.

30:35.964 --> 30:39.620
I DON'T KNOW WHETHER TO BE
HORRIFIED OR JUST PLAIN JEALOUS.

30:41.448 --> 30:45.452
-THAT'S YOUR RESPONSE?
-NO, THIS IS MY RESPONSE.

30:45.582 --> 30:47.497
WE'RE AT WAR.

30:47.628 --> 30:50.109
WE ARE FIGHTING FOR
A BILLION DOLLARS WORTH OF COAL.

30:50.239 --> 30:51.675
IT'S REALLY SIMPLE, NED.

30:51.806 --> 30:54.591
EITHER YOU WANT US TO WIN
THE WAR, OR YOU DON'T.

30:54.722 --> 30:56.376
-HE THREATENED MY FAMILY.

30:56.506 --> 30:59.988
-THE ONLY THREAT TO YOUR FAMILY
I SEE RIGHT NOW IS YOU.

31:03.513 --> 31:06.386
-WHAT ARE YOU TALKIN' ABOUT?!
HE...

31:06.516 --> 31:08.867
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?
I SHOULD JUST LET HIM SHOOT ME?

31:08.997 --> 31:12.827
HUH? AND KILL MY WIFE AND CHILD?
THEY'RE ALL THAT I'VE GOT.

31:12.958 --> 31:14.960
BUT YOU WOULDN'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT,

31:15.090 --> 31:16.309
YOU COLD LITTLE BITCH!

31:20.008 --> 31:21.836
-YOU'RE GONNA BE
LEAVING US NOW, NED.

31:27.015 --> 31:30.192
YOU ENJOY THE REST
OF YOUR SUNDAY.

31:30.323 --> 31:33.630
[ FOOTSTEPS DEPART ]

31:33.761 --> 31:37.939
-[ MOANING ]

31:38.070 --> 31:40.115
MM-HMM. [ INHALES SHARPLY ]

31:40.246 --> 31:43.640
UH-HUH. UH-HUH. [ MOANS ] MM.

31:43.771 --> 31:46.730
-RICKI, MY BACK HURTS.

31:46.861 --> 31:49.820
♪♪

31:52.388 --> 31:53.999
-[ SIGHS ]

31:56.566 --> 31:58.090
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]

31:58.220 --> 31:59.918
-YOU SMELL LIKE BACON.

32:00.048 --> 32:03.922
-YEAH, I WAS COOKING BREAKFAST
FOR MY BOY.

32:04.052 --> 32:08.448
-"IF YOU CAN'T CUT THE MUSTARD,
YOU COULD ALWAYS LICK THE JAR."

32:08.578 --> 32:11.233
I HEARD THAT IN A SONG, I THINK.
YOU KNOW WHAT SONG THAT IS?

32:11.364 --> 32:12.756
-NO.

32:12.887 --> 32:15.803
-I GOT SOMETHING FOR THAT BACK,
BY THE WAY.

32:15.934 --> 32:19.154
AND SOME TEQUILA.

32:19.285 --> 32:21.461
-NO, THANK YOU.

32:21.591 --> 32:24.943
-REALLY? I THOUGHT YOU SAID
YOU WERE HAVING A BAD DAY.

32:25.073 --> 32:28.033
-I WAS UP ALL NIGHT
JUST WORRYING ABOUT CALEB.

32:28.163 --> 32:30.426
[ DRAWER OPENS ]
-[ GRUNTS ]

32:30.557 --> 32:33.473
-OF COURSE, HE SLEPT LIKE A LOG.
-[ CHUCKLES ]

32:33.603 --> 32:35.344
[ PILLS RATTLE ]
MM?

32:35.475 --> 32:38.391
[ DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

32:38.521 --> 32:41.785
-JUST TRYING TO SEE THINGS
A LITTLE...

32:41.916 --> 32:44.832
BIT CLEARLY FOR A WHILE.

32:44.963 --> 32:46.051
[ BOTTLE CLATTERS ]
-YEAH.

32:46.181 --> 32:48.009
[ PILLS RATTLE ]

32:48.140 --> 32:49.968
THAT'S GOOD.

32:50.098 --> 32:51.795
A NEW LEAF.

32:51.926 --> 32:54.146
I CAN RESPECT THAT.

32:54.276 --> 32:56.148
DON'T MIND ME.

32:56.278 --> 33:01.283
-[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

33:06.854 --> 33:11.946
-I GOT SOME FENNIGAN.
IT'LL TAKE THE EDGE OFF.

33:14.122 --> 33:15.384
-NO.

33:23.001 --> 33:26.004
-BOOP. BOOP, BOOP, BOOP.

33:26.134 --> 33:27.831
DOO, DOO.

33:27.962 --> 33:30.399
-CUT IT OUT.

33:30.530 --> 33:33.272
[ SIGHS DEEPLY ]

33:33.402 --> 33:35.100
♪♪

33:35.230 --> 33:39.017
-BOOP, BOOP, BOOP.

33:39.147 --> 33:41.106
BOOP.

33:41.236 --> 33:42.585
♪♪

33:42.716 --> 33:43.978
BOOP.

33:44.109 --> 33:58.210
♪♪

33:58.340 --> 34:01.300
[ ENGINES RUMBLING ]

34:27.543 --> 34:29.284
-REMEMBER THIS DAY, BOYS.

34:29.415 --> 34:33.506
TODAY BE THE DAY
GUARANTEES OUR VERY SURVIVAL.

34:33.636 --> 34:37.031
IN YOUR NAME AND HONOR, FA.

34:37.162 --> 34:39.381
-GED-GEDYAH.

34:42.384 --> 34:45.387
[ ENGINES RUMBLING ]

34:59.749 --> 35:02.361
[ ENGINES TURN OFF ]

35:04.928 --> 35:08.410
-ALL RIGHT, THAT SHOULD BE EASY
TO POP. GET IN THERE, BOY.

35:15.243 --> 35:17.463
-GET OUT OF HERE!

35:17.593 --> 35:18.768
[ GUNSHOTS ]

35:18.899 --> 35:21.293
[ RAPID GUNFIRE ]

35:21.423 --> 35:23.643
[ GLASS SHATTERING ]

35:41.226 --> 35:43.053
-WHAT WE GONNA DO, FOSTER?

35:43.184 --> 35:45.404
♪♪

35:50.757 --> 35:54.152
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

35:54.282 --> 35:58.373
[ RING ]

35:58.504 --> 36:01.159
[ RING ]

36:01.289 --> 36:04.423
[ RING ]
-WADE.

36:04.553 --> 36:06.468
-HUH?
[ RING ]

36:06.599 --> 36:08.775
-YOUR PHONE.
-[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

36:08.905 --> 36:11.604
[ RING,
DOG BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

36:11.734 --> 36:13.214
[ MOANS ]
[ RING ]

36:13.345 --> 36:15.782
[ SIGHS ]
-OH.

36:15.912 --> 36:17.131
[ RING ]
-[ SIGHS ]

36:17.262 --> 36:20.178
-[ GROANS ]
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

36:20.308 --> 36:22.571
-WADE HOUGHTON.

36:22.702 --> 36:24.617
-LEAVE IT.

36:26.096 --> 36:28.229
-WHAT?

36:28.360 --> 36:29.796
YEAH, I'M RIGHT NEAR THERE.
I'M COMING DOWN.

36:29.926 --> 36:32.929
♪♪

36:36.716 --> 36:39.588
[ ENGINE STARTS ]

36:39.719 --> 36:42.591
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

36:42.722 --> 36:46.334
[ SIREN WAILING, TIRES PEAL ]

36:51.426 --> 36:54.821
[ GUNFIRE ]

36:54.951 --> 36:56.866
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

36:56.997 --> 36:58.868
[ GUNFIRE CONTINUES ]

36:58.999 --> 37:01.175
-HOLY HELL.
THEY GOT THEM A CANNON.

37:01.306 --> 37:03.482
[ GUNSHOTS ]

37:05.266 --> 37:07.964
-[ PANTING ]
[ GUNSHOT ]

37:09.618 --> 37:13.056
[ GUNSHOTS CONTINUE ]

37:13.187 --> 37:14.667
-GO, GO, GO, GO, GO, GO, GO.

37:14.797 --> 37:18.279
[ GUNSHOTS CONTINUE ]

37:21.282 --> 37:23.328
-THEY GOT WEAPONS
TO KINGDOM COME, PA.

37:23.458 --> 37:26.940
I KNOW YOU SAID HOLD YOUR FIRE,
BUT I AIN'T GOT NO FIRE LEFT.

37:27.070 --> 37:30.378
-ALL RIGHT, THEN WE QUIT.

37:30.509 --> 37:32.250
[ Whispers ]
WE QUIT. GOT NO CHOICE.

37:32.380 --> 37:34.164
[ Normal voice ] ALL RIGHT,

37:34.295 --> 37:37.124
SHAME ON THE NAME OF MY FA,
BUT WE GOT NO CHOICE.

37:37.255 --> 37:39.866
ALL RIGHT, WE QUIT! WE QUIT!

37:39.996 --> 37:42.042
-TOSS OUT YOUR GUNS
SO WE CAN SEE 'EM!

37:42.172 --> 37:43.348
-[ GRUNTS ] ALL RIGHT.

37:43.478 --> 37:44.653
RIGHT -- RIGHT THERE.
YOU SEE THAT?

37:44.784 --> 37:46.046
RIGHT THERE. OKAY?

37:46.176 --> 37:48.614
-THAT BETTER BE ALL OF 'EM!

37:48.744 --> 37:50.703
-YES, SIR. RIGHT THERE.

37:50.833 --> 37:52.487
THAT'S THE LOT OF THEM, OKAY?

37:52.618 --> 37:53.749
THAT'S THE LOT.

37:53.880 --> 37:55.142
-STAND UP

37:55.273 --> 37:57.492
AND PUT YOUR HANDS
UP ON YOUR HEAD!

37:57.623 --> 37:59.277
-I AIN'T QUIT.

37:59.407 --> 38:01.279
-DON'T YOU BE A FOOL.

38:01.409 --> 38:05.065
-YOU'RE GONNA GET US ALL SHOT.
-THEY AIN'T TAKIN' ME.

38:05.195 --> 38:07.937
-GET OUT HERE NOW!
OR I'LL COME OUT AND GET YA!

38:08.068 --> 38:10.810
AND THERE WON'T BE
NO DAMN MERCY INVOLVED!

38:10.940 --> 38:12.812
-[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

38:12.942 --> 38:15.815
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

38:15.945 --> 38:17.251
-WE GOT 'EM, SHERIFF.

38:17.382 --> 38:18.774
-HUH? WHERE ARE THEY?
ARE THEY IN THERE?

38:18.905 --> 38:21.908
-THEY'RE OUT THERE!

38:22.038 --> 38:24.650
-[ Whispers ] HEY.

38:24.780 --> 38:26.608
-OKAY, STAND DOWN.
-WHAT?

38:26.739 --> 38:28.218
-PUT YOUR GUNS DOWN.
-BUT, SHERIFF -- WHAT?!

38:28.349 --> 38:29.568
-I'M TELLING YOU RIGHT NOW.
-[ SHOUTS INDISTINCTLY ]

38:29.698 --> 38:31.439
-I'M TELLING YOU,
I JUST SAID STAND DOWN.

38:31.570 --> 38:34.224
-WE'RE CLEAR, BOYS.

38:34.355 --> 38:36.705
-LET'S GO.

38:36.836 --> 38:38.751
-THEY'RE GETTIN' AWAY.
THEY'RE...THEY'RE GETTIN' AWAY!

38:38.881 --> 38:43.277
[ ENGINES REVVING ]

38:43.408 --> 38:45.192
[ GUNSHOTS ]
-GODDAMN IT, HIRAM!

38:45.323 --> 38:48.021
I JUST TOLD YOU NO MORE FIRING!
-LET ME GO!

38:48.151 --> 38:49.675
-I JUST SAID THAT!

38:49.805 --> 38:51.372
-WELL, GO AFTER THEM!
-I'M GOIN' AFTER THEM, HIRAM!

38:51.503 --> 38:53.243
I JUST SAID THAT
I'M GOING AFTER THEM!

38:53.374 --> 38:55.463
-HEY, WHAT KIND OF SHERIFF
ARE YOU ANYWAY?

38:55.594 --> 38:58.553
[ SIREN WAILING ]

39:14.264 --> 39:16.310
[ SIREN CONTINUES WAILING ]

39:16.441 --> 39:20.096
[ ENGINES REVVING ]

39:22.185 --> 39:25.972
[ SIREN CONTINUES WAILING,
TIRES SCREECH ]

39:31.717 --> 39:34.633
[ ENGINE IDLING ]

39:36.461 --> 39:37.766
[ ENGINE REVVING ]

39:37.897 --> 39:41.640
[ SIREN CONTINUES WAILING ]

39:41.770 --> 39:44.077
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

39:56.611 --> 40:00.920
[ SIREN CONTINUES WAILING ]

40:07.970 --> 40:09.537
[ SIREN STOPS WAILING,
ENGINE REVVING ]

40:12.148 --> 40:15.935
-Aw! Shit, sheriff, I lost them.
You need backup?

40:16.065 --> 40:17.893
-NEGATIVE. LOST MINE, TOO.

40:18.024 --> 40:20.983
[ SIREN WAILING ]

40:22.724 --> 40:25.727
[ SIREN STOPS WAILING,
ENGINES REVVING ]

40:34.344 --> 40:37.391
[ THE LOUVIN BROTHERS'
"THE KNEELING DRUNKARD'S PLEA" ]

40:40.699 --> 40:46.182
♪ LORD, HAVE MERCY ON ME

40:46.313 --> 40:51.449
♪ WAS THE KNEELING DRUNKARD'S
PLEA ♪

40:51.579 --> 40:57.193
♪ AND AS HE KNELT THERE
ON THE GROUND ♪

40:57.324 --> 41:04.331
♪ I KNOW THAT GOD FROM HEAVEN
LOOKED DOWN ♪

41:04.462 --> 41:09.815
♪ I WENT DOWN
BY AN OLD COUNTRY CHURCH ♪

41:09.945 --> 41:15.603
♪ I SAW THE DRUNKARD
STAGGER AND LURCH ♪

41:15.734 --> 41:17.126
♪ AND AS HE --

41:17.257 --> 41:21.304
[ LOUD CRASH, THUD ]

41:21.435 --> 41:24.960
-[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

41:25.091 --> 41:28.050
[ CAR ALERT DINGING ]

41:33.708 --> 41:35.493
YOU ALL RIGHT?

41:35.623 --> 41:38.583
[ CONTINUES BREATHING HEAVILY ]

41:40.802 --> 41:42.412
HELLO?

41:42.543 --> 41:45.503
[ CONTINUES BREATHING HEAVILY ]

41:57.079 --> 42:00.735
♪♪

42:12.573 --> 42:16.098
-[ GROANING ]
